<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="999" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="999_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道是誰<delay20 />
把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
放在我的長跑路線上，<delay20 />不過還挺有膽量的嘛！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會<delay20 />是想叫我用它
想出全新的健身清單吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />我接受這項挑戰！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="999_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說最近<delay20 />很流行用放在外面的<delay8 />
東西來鍛鍊肌肉喔！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />使用<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay8 />
以帥氣姿勢鍛鍊肌肉的我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不得了！<delay20 />我興奮起來啦——！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="999_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然會在<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
附近和你碰面<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難不成，<delay20 />我們都被這東西
給吸引過來了嗎！？<delay40 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />不可能吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快看！<delay20 /><20_2 arg="9" />有蘑菇耶！<delay frames="40" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />啊，<delay20 />可惜！！<delay frames="30" />原來是假的啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay20 />是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay frames="30" />
我一瞬間<delay8 />還以為是真的蘑菇，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不小心慌張了一下啊──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說<20_2 arg="9" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />……<delay20 />
看起來冰冰涼涼的耶！！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這下正好，<delay8 />我才剛環島跑完100圈，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拿來做緩和運動剛剛好──！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><delay20 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊～<delay frames="30" />
我想想，<delay20 />該拿它來鍛鍊哪個部位咧？<delay frames="40" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你說這不是用來健身的？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要在這放<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay frames="30" />
就好像回到小時候一樣，<delay8 />
讓人有種興奮的感覺吧？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一聽到積木，<delay8 />
我就會忍不住一直想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要用它來玩什麼遊戲？<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底是誰啊？<delay20 />竟然
把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />放在這！<10_4 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道<delay20 />這是用來裝飾的嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼嘛，<delay20 />把這麼老舊的東西擺在這，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我還以為<delay8 />這個肯定是
沒人要的東西啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果上的是這種<delay20 />在外面擺
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的學校，<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" />感覺讀起書來也會很順利耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />不過這裡沒有屋頂，<delay8 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是下雨會變成落湯雞的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要擺個<delay frames="30" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
就有種<delay8 />身處度假勝地的感覺啊──！！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />其實這裡原本
只是座無人島<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />……<delay20 />
不知道能不能用它來研究出新的健身清單啊？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay20 />那麼……<delay8 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先是深蹲！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來是伏地挺身<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等，<delay20 /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣根本沒用到它啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要擺了<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，
就會有種身處戶外的感覺耶！<delay frames="30" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這狂野的風格<delay8 />真是帥呆啦──！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道啦！<delay frames="40" />
<20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種東西<delay8 />通常會用「可愛」<delay20 />來形容吧？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我搞不懂<delay20 />關鍵的<delay8 />「可愛」是什麼意思啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是用肌肉來比喻的話，<delay8 />
會是什麼肌啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惡──！！<delay20 />到底是誰啦！<delay frames="30" />
竟然把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
擺在這種地方──！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別在我<delay8 />剛好口渴的時候，<delay20 />
把這麼像的東西擺在這啦──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣<delay8 />不是害我更口渴了嗎！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />你不覺得<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很帥氣嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然看起來有點老舊，<delay20 />
但這反而是它的迷人之處啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔～～<delay20 />真浪漫啊──！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看！<delay20 /><20_2 arg="9" />
是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />耶──！<delay frames="40" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />這東西真令人感到興奮啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著它就會不自覺地忘了時間！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />我是不會忘記
健身時間的！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />這裡竟然擺著
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay frames="30" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" />有種置身海裡的感覺耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />
之前<delay8 />我的泳圈掉了的時候，<delay frames="30" />
看到的景色就是這種感覺喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種東西通常都會用<delay20 />
很有摩登感、很時尚來形容吧？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />要是在島上的戶外<delay20 />擺著這種東西，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許會出乎意料地帥氣喔──！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay40 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" />看起來<delay8 />像是用蛋做的。<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道是用真的蛋做的？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是真的，那是用什麼蛋咧<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay20 />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會是恐龍蛋吧？！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚喔喔——！<delay8 />好帥啊——！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay8 />
外面的<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
是我放的嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然那東西<delay8 />
看起來應該是我做的沒錯，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我完全想不起來啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />只要擺了<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<20_2 arg="9" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會對外太空或其他星球心生嚮往啊——！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />外太空沒有重力，<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以應該不適合健身啦——<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />問你喔，如果想要用
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />健身，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得做哪種運動會比較好？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay8 />這不是為了健身才擺在這裡的？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay8 />但基本上不管是什麼東西，<delay8 />
我都能夠用來健身啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是誰把從海裡撈上來的東西<delay20 />
放在外面不管的？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay8 />不是這樣啊？<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼嘛，<delay8 />我看上面黏著貝殼，<delay20 />
還以為一定是這樣子，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
是依星座的樣子製作的對吧？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，不管我怎麼看<delay20 />
這都不像是星星的形狀啊？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />想不通，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />有<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />……
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道說，<delay8 />這東西
本來是在海裡面嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是這樣，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想打撈這傢伙上來時，<delay8 />
手臂肌肉一定<delay8 />
派上了很大的用場，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像有人看到這個<delay8 />能感受到
其中的「風情」，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我只感受得到
適合運動的秋天啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />你看，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="9" />這裡有
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />喔！<delay40 />
<20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會有鬼怪跑出來吧？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是沒在怕啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是偶爾會聽到<delay8 />南瓜鬼之類的，<delay20 />
剛好想到而已啦——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是誰啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
就這樣丟在外面。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是玩完後<delay8 />不收好，<delay20 />到時候被媽媽罵
我可不管喔？<delay40 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使到了現在，<delay8 />
我還是很常在夢中被罵啊。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會不自覺地<delay20 />想吃些
好吃的東西喔。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是訓練後吃的餐點，<delay8 />這個特別重要！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />俗話說良好的飲食<delay8 />
能造就健美的肌肉嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啦，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
來跟上我的動作吧！！<delay40 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay8 />你問我為什麼突然說這些？<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然這種地方擺著<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然就要展現熱情，<delay8 />盡情跳舞啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />這個<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />給人一種充滿謎團的感覺啊。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我對這方面不太懂，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但總覺得能感受到某種浪漫喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>